Welcome to Media. At allstar camp, we look forward to learning as much about you as we can. That's why we ask all of you to tell us more about yourself here.We're really excited about all of your input, so don't be shy. But for the most part you don't have to change your profile to give us your info. You're welcome to show up on just about anywhere, chat with you team or attend a few practices through the weekend – we just ask that you send us a photo before you head out to your video shoot.We get EVEN MORE email from you as the All Star camp gets closer, so please be sure to check your email. After all, it just might be the best news you'll read all year.
